<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p> <rs type="material">White marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">relief</rs> panels  from a monumental public tomb, with sculpted <rs type="decoration">figure</rs>s ; <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">1.85</measure>; width of panels <measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.75</measure>-<measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">1.30</measure>. The maximum depth of the panels is <measure dim="depth" type="length" unit="metre">0.40</measure>-<measure dim="depth" type="length" unit="metre">0.50</measure>.</p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the face next to the figures. Numbers for fitting the blocks survive (<measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.02</measure>-<measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.03</measure>) normally on the upper face of the blocks, but in some cases on the face. </p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Description of Letters</head>
<p><measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.04-0.05</measure></p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="date">
 <head>Date</head>

<p> <date exact="none" notAfter="0100" notBefore="0067">Late first century A.D.</date> (<rs type="criteria">career</rs>, <rs type="criteria">sculpture</rs>, <rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>)</p></div>

